229
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:11,740
It does feel nice.

230
00:12:11,740 --> 00:12:13,606
It's all thanks to Gan Yang.

231
00:12:13,606 --> 00:12:16,300
He will come later. We'd better watch our words.

232
00:12:16,300 --> 00:12:19,540
You mean Director Gan, right?

233
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:22,680
Honestly, his cold face this morning scared me.

234
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:24,900
I really feared he'd break with us.

235
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:27,100
