238
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:33,860
 If he does cut ties with us, who will test all that junk of his? 

239
00:12:33,860 --> 00:12:35,780
 Buddy, keep your voice down. 

240
00:12:35,780 --> 00:12:37,560
