242
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,840
 Rotten shoes are rotten shoes. 

243
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,520
 Why can't we say that? 

244
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:45,540
 You still defend them after all they did? 

245
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:48,180
 They act nice to your face, but do you know what they say behind your back? 

246
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:50,280
 They say you'll never make good shoes. 

247
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:52,060
