249
00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:56,400
True. What's taking him so long?

250
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:58,440
Here he is.

251
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,820
- Director Gan. 
 - Director Gan.

252
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:00,980
