256
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:08,960
When the next version comes out, we're happy to test them.

257
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,100
That's not necessary.

258
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:14,240
I won't trouble you with such small things anymore.

259
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,040
Come on, we're buddies.

260
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:19,260
We're more than willing to help you.

261
00:13:19,260 --> 00:13:22,260
Director Gan, what's that in your hands?

262
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:23,380
This?

263
