00:33:26,280 --> 00:33:27,480
Don't you love meat?

608
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:30,060
I made you a steak, medium rare.

609
00:33:34,060 --> 00:33:36,260
All right, get to the point.

610
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,780
Do you know how to fix a laptop?

611
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:41,600
Take a look.

612
00:33:45,360 --> 00:33:47,320
Whose is this? It's so old.

613
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:48,900
It's been used for ages.

614
00:33:48,900 --> 00:33:49,940
It's Ding Zhi Tong's.

615
00:33:49,940 --> 00:33:51,820
I guessed that.

616
00:33:51,820 --> 00:33:54,500
Buddy, other people chase girls with flowers and jewelry.

617
00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:56,380
You always do such stuff.

618
00:33:56,380 --> 00:33:59,260
Shut up. Can you fix it or not?

